race.comment: ATMOSPHERE (3) has a handy record over this distance range with three wins and eight placings from 14 attempts and will be high on confidence following that dominant Sunny Coast victory last time out. Race has lost most of his anticipated main rivals so can easily go back-to-back without surprising. BADGERS NUTS (5) is a six-time winner over this journey and will be ready to peak now fourth-up from the break. In the mix. INVER PARK (2) produced the best run of his latest campaign when third at the Sunshine Coast. FAKE MAGIC (7) has struck form at his past two starts. Won at Dalby two starts back and then ran fourth at Warwick.
